Paper: 0012414
Title: Uniform semiclassical approximation in quantum statistical mechanics
Authors: C. A. A. de Carvalho and R. M. Cavalcanti and E. S. Fraga and S. E. Joras
Abstract: We present a simple method to deal with caustics in the semiclassical approximation to the partition function of a one-dimensional quantum system. The procedure, which makes use of complex trajectories, is applied to the quartic double-well potential.
